de.brands4friends.daleq.core

Interface RowData


  • public interface RowData
    A data holding entity which represents a table row according to Daleq's data model. This class is used internally by Daleq and should not be accessed directly by clients.
    See Also:
    TableData, FieldData

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean containsField(java.lang.String fieldName)
      Returns true, if such a field exists, otherwise false.
      FieldData getFieldBy(java.lang.String fieldName)
      If the row contains a Field with the given fieldName, the respective FieldData is returned.

    • Method Detail

      • getFieldBy

        FieldData getFieldBy(java.lang.String fieldName)
        If the row contains a Field with the given fieldName, the respective FieldData is returned.
        Parameters:
        fieldName - the name of a field, which should exist in the respective row.
        Throws:
        NoSuchDaleqFieldException - if such a field does not exist in the RowData
